{
  "chapter": 30,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十回 断臂论交\n\n楚留香与姬冰雁发现石观音弟子的尸体都被削去了眉毛，推断是画眉鸟所为。画眉鸟似乎是为了帮助楚留香而杀人，但动机不明。众人离开秘谷时，胡铁花突然出现并砍断了一点红的左臂。得知真相后，胡铁花愧疚欲自断手臂偿还，但被姬冰雁劝阻。一点红反而称赞胡铁花刀法，并表示这笔账不需要还。\n\n琵琶公主、柳别飞等人与楚留香会合。楚留香似乎领悟了什么禅机，对石观音的下落表现得胸有成竹。他拒绝了柳别飞的告辞请求，暗示华山七剑与石观音之间有隐秘关联。最后众人听到驼铃声，却发现骆驼队戒备森严，气氛紧张。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你仔细瞧瞧她们的脸。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我不喜欢看女人，活的都不看，何况死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你若仔细一瞧，就可发现她们各个的死法虽不向，但却有一样相同之处。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，这些少女都没有眉毛。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "她们本来是有眉毛的，只不过被人削去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道他杀人之前，先要将别人的眉毛削去么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这只怕就是画眉鸟杀人的标布，看来他不但以杀人为享乐，而且还要使人都知道，人是他杀的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但他这次杀人却是为了你，好歹总帮了你的忙，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他为什么要帮你的忙?你认得他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他总不会无缘无故的，来了就杀人，杀了人就走?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "这其中自然有原因。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么原因?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "到目前为止，我简直连一点迹象都猜不出，但我相信，无论他的用心是好是坏，都不会就此一走了之的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你想……他不久会现身么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "说不定他时时刻刻都在等我们，只是我们都瞧不见他罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "像这样的人，我倒宁可永远莫要瞧见他才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但无论如何，现在石观音的弟子，总算已死尽死绝了，我们已可大大方方的走出去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "小胡，是你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "除了我这倒楣鬼还有谁?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好家伙，老臭虫你可真有两下子，但若非我已累得半死了，你们也休想这么快就得手。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你们没有杀了我，本该谢天谢地才是，为什么……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "刚刚……刚刚……刚刚……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你刚刚真是闯出祸来了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是谁受了伤?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "好刀法。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你不必难受，这不能怪你，我若是你，也得砍这一刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你可知道他是谁么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "我只知道他是条好汉，天下少见的好汉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "他就是一点红。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "中原一点红?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "text": "我真该死!该死!该死!",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你用不着这样做。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "你放手，我用不着你管。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你可知道，不只是你欠他一只手，我也欠他一条腿，但我们用不着现在急着就还他，以后等他需要时再还，岂非更好么?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "这笔账，但愿你能还得清才好。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这不是账，谁也用不着还的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_dian_hong",
      "speaker_name": "一点红",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这只手反正已杀得太多了，让它休息休息也好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "画眉鸟，这小子究竟是什么人?可真是心狠手辣。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他喜欢杀人，为什么不索性将石观音也一齐杀了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "也许他恰巧没有遇见石观音，也许他还要将石观音留给楚留香。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "text": "石观音又怎会恰巧不在呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_bing_yan",
      "speaker_name": "姬冰雁",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "据这位曲姑娘说，石观音并不是常常都在那里的，尤其是最近，她不在的时候，反而比在的时候多得多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么，平时她在什么地方呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么不说话呀?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你知道石观音在哪里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "石观音?谁是石观音?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你想什么想得发了呆，连石观音都忘了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "有石观音即是没有石观音，没有石观音即是有石观音……我从来也不曾记得，却叫我从何忘记?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这是什么话?我不懂。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你本来就不懂，这是禅机。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么禅机?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "天机不可泄漏，佛云：不可说，不可说。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你打什么机锋?忽然想做和尚了吗?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我正是忽然想起个和尚来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "谁?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你说的不错，这人有时实在可恨得很。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极乐之星现在在哪里?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我本来已交给她，她又还给我了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你若真是知道了这极乐之星的秘密，又当如何?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我既然已答应了王妃，自然要告诉她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "很好，我们现在就去找她吧!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但……但石观音呢?",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "石观音?谁是石观音?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你这人究竟在打什么主意?",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你跟我去，就会明白了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在下兄弟已有十余年未返华山，此刻楚香帅既然要去办别的事，在下兄弟就想……就想告辞了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "两位现在还不能走。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅莫非还有什么吩咐么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "两位跟我去就会明白了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在下只求楚香帅答应一件事。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "柳兄又有何吩咐?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "在下倒无妨，但有些事，却是我皇甫大哥不愿说出，甚至连提都不愿提起的……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "但我若问起这些事，你们又不能不说，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "正是如此，所以，在下只求楚香帅……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "你要我连问都莫问，是么?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "香帅若肯答应，在下实是感激不尽。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "我现在可曾问过什么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "什么都未曾问起。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "现在既未曾问，以后还会问么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，香帅现在既然还没有问，以后更不会问了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "你明白就好。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "speaker_name": "柳别飞",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但这些事，香帅本该问的，为何又不问了呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_liu_bie_fei",
      "text": "只因我该问的，我已知道了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你该问什么?你又知道什么?求求你，莫要打哑谜好么?",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你可知道那是什么声音?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "在沙漠上，我就算是个没见过世面的乡巴佬，但那声音我还是听得出来的……那是驼铃声，对不对?",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "那不是驼铃声。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不是驼铃声?是什么声音?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pi_pa_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "琵琶公主",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "在我耳中听来，那简直就像是水往杯子里倒的声音，肉在火上烤的声音……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 30,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    }
